# Image assets directory
# This directory contains the default background images for the theme

# Default background images included:
# - home-bg.jpg (homepage background) - Beautiful landscape
# - about-bg.jpg (about page background) - Workspace/notebook scene
# - post-bg.jpg (post page background) - Writing/keyboard scene
# - contact-bg.jpg (contact page background) - Communication theme

# Images are sourced from Unsplash and optimized for web
# Recommended image size: 1900x1200px
# File format: JPG (optimized for faster loading)

# To customize:
# 1. Replace these files with your own images
# 2. Keep the same filenames, or
# 3. Update the _config.yml file with new paths